The grounds put forth by the appellant in support of this appeal can be summarized as:

(a) whether the Tribunal erred in concluding that s 72B(1),

Cap 57

was applicable to the respondent’s claim;

(b) if the answer to sub-para (a) above is in the affirmative, whether the respondent was dismissed for a valid reason (s 32K,

Cap 57

);

(c) whether the appellant’s staff manual formed part of the respondent’s employment contract with the appellant.

